<英文法規名稱>Regulations for the Declaration of Carrying Foreign Currencies or Securities by Cross-Border Passengers or Service Crew on Board of Transport and for the Interagency Report by the Customs</英文法規名稱>
<中文法規名稱>旅客或隨交通工具服務之人員出入國境攜帶外幣現鈔或有價證券申報及通報辦法</中文法規名稱>
